title: XP Drivers for Dell Inspiron 1525
description:

This torrent includes:

Chipset Drivers
Sigmatel HD Audio Drivers
Video Card Drivers
Dell Quickset Utilities
Ricoh Drivers
Dell Touchpad Drivers
Dell WLAN Wifi Network Card Drivers

All of these Drivers have been tested and work on Windows XP SP2 or later.

**Note: These drivers are for the Dell Inspiron 1525 with XP not Vista.**

Let me know if you are having any problems, and I will try to help you the best I can.
